The overall objective of this proposal is to strengthen the Presidency so that it can adequately carry out its role of supporting the President in his task of running his Cabinet, and through this support the functioning of the Government of Southern Sudan, contributing to democratic development and sustainable peace. 

The programme will give rise to the following outputs:

1) The President has access to timely, high quality, independent political and economic analysis;
2) The President has timely, high quality, and succinct briefing papers on all matters of interest;
3) An effective Communications and Press Office; and
4) All Offices of the Presidency are efficiently and effectively managed
